<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Who is actually controlling Bitcoin?</h3>



<p>While Bitcoin&#8217;s decentralized nature means no single entity holds the reins, Dogecoin&#8217;s compliance landscape is influenced by a community-driven governance structure. </p>



